A4.text: Egypt's election commission announced that Muslim Brotherhood candidate Mohamed Morsi had won Egypt's presidential elections.

A5.text: Morsi won by a narrow margin over Ahmed Shafik, the final prime minister under deposed President Hosni Mubarak.
